    {
      "action": "create incident",
      "identifier": "create_incident",
      "description": "Create Radar Privacy Incident",
      "verbose": "<p>This action creates a privacy incident in Radar using the following phantom system and app configurations:</p>\n<h4>Company Settings</h4>\n<p><b>Base URL For Phantom Appliance</b> - used to link the created incident's 'intake method' to this instance of Phantom.</p>\n\n<h4>Asset Configuration</h4>\n<p>Asset configuration values are used as follows to create the incident:</p>\n<p><b>Incident Group ID</b> - must be specified in the asset configuration for authorization.</p>\n<p><b>Time Zone</b> - the current moment that this action is triggered is used to set the created incident's 'discovered' date and time. The asset <b>Time Zone</b> is used to specify the 'discovered' time zone offset.</p>\n\n\n<h4>Container Information</h4>\n<p>The container ID for the associated phantom event or case is use to specify the Radar incident channel ID. This is used to associate the created incident to the container</p>\n\n<h4>Action Parameters</h4>\n<p>The action parameters are used to set the Radar incident <b>name</b> and <b>description</b></p>\n",
      "type": "generic",
      "read_only": false,
      "parameters": {
        "name": {
          "description": "A name summarizing the privacy incident",
          "data_type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "default": "",
          "order": 0
        },
        "description": {
          "description": "A description of the privacy incident (plain text only",
          "data_type": "string",
          "order": 1
        }
      },
      "output": [
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.incident_id",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "incident id",
          "column_order": 0,
          "contains": [
            "radar incident id"
          ]
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.name",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "incident name",
          "column_order": 1
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.description",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "incident description",
          "column_order": 2
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.incident_group",
          "data_type": "numeric",
          "column_name": "incident group id",
          "column_order": 3
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.url",
          "data_type": "numeric",
          "column_name": "incident group id",
          "column_order": 4
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.status",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "status",
          "column_order": 5
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.message",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_order": 6
        }
      ],
      "render": {
        "type": "custom",
        "view": "radar_view.display_privacy_incident",
        "title": "Privacy Incident",
        "menu_name": "Radar Privacy Incident"
      },
      "versions": "EQ(*)"
    },
    {
      "action": "add note",
      "identifier": "add_note",
      "description": "Add a Note to a Radar Privacy Incident",
      "verbose": "<p>This action adds a note to a given Radar incident using the following configurations:</p>\n\n<h4>Action Parameters</h4>\n<p><b>Incident ID</b> - used to add a note to a given incident</p>\n<p><b>Content</b> - the content of the note</p>\n\n\n<h4>Note Category</h4>\n<p>The note category will always be set to 'Splunk Phantom'</p>",
      "type": "generic",
      "read_only": false,
      "parameters": {
        "incident_id": {
          "description": "Radar Incident ID",
          "data_type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "order": 0,
          "contains": [
            "radar incident id"
          ],
          "primary": true
        },
        "content": {
          "description": "Note content",
          "data_type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "order": 1
        }
      },
      "output": [
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.id",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "note id",
          "column_order": 0,
          "contains": [
            "radar note id"
          ]
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.incident_id",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "incident id",
          "column_order": 1,
          "contains": [
            "radar incident id"
          ]
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.content",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "note content",
          "column_order": 2
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.data.*.category",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "note category",
          "column_order": 3
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.status",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_name": "status",
          "column_order": 4
        },
        {
          "data_path": "action_result.message",
          "data_type": "string",
          "column_order": 5
        }
      ],
      "render": {
        "type": "custom",
        "view": "radar_view.display_privacy_incident_note",
        "title": "Privacy Incident Note",
        "menu_name": "Radar Privacy Incident Note"
      },
      "versions": "EQ(*)"
    }
